<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Whirlwind" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Whirlwind,</orth> a furious tempest: <cit><quote>my sighs, like --s, labour hence to heave thee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 586" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 586</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that some w. bear unto a ragged rock,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.2.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 2, 120</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as --s shake fair buds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.140" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. V, 2, 140</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.288" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 288</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 4, 60</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>